{"tha-ap144:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap144:0.2":"Chattavagga ","tha-ap144:0.3":"Thambharopakattheraapadana ","tha-ap144:1.1":"“Nibbute lokanathamhi, ","tha-ap144:1.2":"dhammadassinarasabhe; ","tha-ap144:1.3":"Aropesim dhajatthambham, ","tha-ap144:1.4":"buddhasetthassa cetiye. ","tha-ap144:2.1":"Nissenim mapayitvana, ","tha-ap144:2.2":"thupasettham samaruhim; ","tha-ap144:2.3":"Jatipuppham gahetvana, ","tha-ap144:2.4":"thupamhi abhiropayim. ","tha-ap144:3.1":"Aho buddha aho dhamma, ","tha-ap144:3.2":"aho no satthu sampada; ","tha-ap144:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap144:3.4":"thupapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap144:4.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap144:4.2":"thupasikhasanamaka; ","tha-ap144:4.3":"Solasasimsu rajano, ","tha-ap144:4.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap144:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap144:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap144:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap144:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma thambharopako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap144:7.1":"Thambharopakattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}